01:13:15,612 --> 01:13:18,212
メロメロめらっぽ　プププくらん
Melo-melo melappo, pu-pu-pu klan

1024
01:13:18,212 --> 01:13:20,812
ぴゅあおししましょう　アップププ
Let's do a pure oshi, ap-pu-pu-pu

1025
01:13:20,812 --> 01:13:23,612
ずっと歌を　見逃さないでしょう？
You won't miss a single song, will you?

1026
01:13:23,612 --> 01:13:26,212
目移りはダメ　本当イヤイヤ
No looking at others, I really hate that

1027
01:13:26,212 --> 01:13:28,812
いつも見て見て　ウォッチも合ってる？
Look at me always, are our eyes meeting?

1028
01:13:28,812 --> 01:13:31,712
あなたが推してくれる愛情の桁
The sheer scale of the love you give me

1029
01:13:31,712 --> 01:13:34,612
私は捧げる　栄養を　さあ！
I'll give you nourishment, come on!

1030
01:13:34,612 --> 01:13:37,212
Love Love Love　後ろ指チュムチュム
Love Love Love, kiss the finger pointed at my back

1031
01:13:37,212 --> 01:13:39,812
とってもとってもとってもとっても　愛して欲しい
I want you to love me very, very, very, very much

1032
01:13:39,812 --> 01:13:42,412
ハピハピハピ　最上級ハギュハギュ
Happy happy happy, the ultimate hug-hug

1033
01:13:42,412 --> 01:13:45,012
おはよおはよおはよ　はっきりはっきりはっきりはっきり
Good morning, good morning, clearly, clearly, clearly, clearly

1034
01:13:45,012 --> 01:13:47,612
ここらへんでしょ　ピコピコ気持ちの
It's around here, isn't it? My piko-piko feelings...

1035
01:13:47,612 --> 01:13:50,212
バロメーターが　超上がる
...barometer is rising like crazy!

1036
01:13:50,212 --> 01:13:53,512
ぴゅあおし！ ぴゅあおし！ ぴゅあおし！
Pure oshi! Pure oshi! Pure oshi!

1037
01:13:53,512 --> 01:13:55,412
もう本当に本当に本当に　わかってね
Really, really, really, please understand

1038
01:13:55,412 --> 01:13:56,612
わかってね
Please understand

1039
01:13:56,612 --> 01:13:59,012
おーいみんな！ ここまでついてこれてる？
Hey everyone! Can you keep up with us so far?

1040
01:13:59,012 --> 01:14:01,412
この後もこの調子でいくよ！
Let's keep going like this!

1041
01:14:01,412 --> 01:14:06,512
うりゃおい！ うりゃおい！
Urya oi! Urya oi!

1042
01:14:06,512 --> 01:14:09,112
ちょっと待ってなんで他の子　褒めるの？
Wait a second, why are you praising other girls?

1043
01:14:09,112 --> 01:14:11,612
よそ見は　プツプツプッ！
No looking away! Snap, snap, snap!

1044
01:14:11,612 --> 01:14:14,412
私が今　気になってるでしょ？
I'm the one you're interested in right now, right?

1045
01:14:14,412 --> 01:14:16,912
ありえないの　ありえない
It's unbelievable, unbelievable

1046
01:14:16,912 --> 01:14:19,512
プンプン　他の子に　チュチュチュだけ
Pouting, just giving kisses to other girls...

1047
01:14:19,512 --> 01:14:22,112
よそ見したよね？　うそマジ無理で
You looked away, didn't you? No way, I seriously can't

1048
01:14:22,112 --> 01:14:24,612
ぴゅあおし死んじゃう　私おこんじゃう
My pure oshi will die, I'm gonna get mad

1049
01:14:24,612 --> 01:14:27,212
指切りしてよ　針千本
Pinky swear with me, or swallow a thousand needles

1050
01:14:27,212 --> 01:14:29,812
心変わりしたら本当に
If you have a change of heart, I'll really...

1051
01:14:29,812 --> 01:14:34,512
拗ねる　怒る　泣いちゃうからね！
...pout, get angry, and cry!

1052
01:14:34,512 --> 01:14:35,412
ズンチャ！
Zuncha!

1053
01:14:35,512 --> 01:14:38,112
ぴゅあおし　してないね？
You aren't doing a pure oshi, are you?

1054
01:14:38,112 --> 01:14:40,712
私だけに　尽くして
Devote yourself only to me

1055
01:14:40,712 --> 01:14:42,412
る（るー）
-ing!

1056
01:14:42,412 --> 01:14:45,012
ダメほらコメントが愛に溢れている
No, look, the comments are overflowing with love

1057
01:14:45,012 --> 01:14:47,612
必死のHP　みるみる回復
My critical HP is recovering instantly

1058
01:14:47,612 --> 01:14:50,212
したよ満ち満ちなパワーじゃん
Look, I'm full of power now!

1059
01:14:50,212 --> 01:14:52,812
ごめごめごめ　ちょごめごめごめ
Sorry, sorry, sorry, a little sorry, sorry, sorry

1060
01:14:52,812 --> 01:14:55,412
Love Love Love　後ろ指チュムチュム
Love Love Love, kiss the finger pointed at my back

1061
01:14:55,412 --> 01:14:58,012
いっぱいっぱいっぱいっぱい　愛して欲しい
I want you to love me so much, so much, so much

1062
01:14:58,012 --> 01:15:00,612
ハピハピハピ　最上級ハギュハギュ
Happy happy happy, the ultimate hug-hug

1063
01:15:00,612 --> 01:15:02,412
うっとりうっとりうっとり
Entranced, entranced, entranced

1064
01:15:02,587 --> 01:15:03,887
コリコリコリコリ...
Kori-kori-kori-kori...

1065
01:15:03,887 --> 01:15:08,587
私のため日々お仕事励んでくれてありがとう
Thank you for working hard every day for my sake

1066
01:15:09,387 --> 01:15:11,187
推しも推しも愛おしい
Both my oshi and your oshi are so precious

1067
01:15:11,387 --> 01:15:15,787
絶対絶対絶対絶対絶対絶対絶対絶対いっぱい
Absolutely, absolutely, absolutely, absolutely, so many times

1068
01:15:15,787 --> 01:15:17,287
お願いね
Please, okay?

1069
01:15:18,187 --> 01:15:20,087
このこのこのこの
This girl, this girl, this girl, this girl

1070
01:15:20,087 --> 01:15:21,987
うー、このこのこのこの
Ooh, this girl, this girl, this girl, this girl

1071
01:15:21,987 --> 01:15:26,087
このこのこのこのこのー！
This girl, this girl, this girl, this girl, this girl!

1072
01:15:26,287 --> 01:15:29,787
銀河の果てまで推してほしい
I want you to support me to the ends of the galaxy

1073
01:15:51,387 --> 01:15:57,187
同じ未来を見ていたい あの夢手にしたい
I want to see the same future, I want to grasp that dream

1074
01:15:57,187 --> 01:16:03,087
それぞれ違った 心で走れよ
Run forward with our individual hearts!

1075
01:16:16,387 --> 01:16:21,987
どこを見ても真っ暗な場所に芽生えてた
It sprouted in a place where everything was pitch black

1076
01:16:21,987 --> 01:16:27,687
ほんの小さな希望に この瞳奪われた
My eyes were captivated by a tiny glimmer of hope

1077
01:16:27,687 --> 01:16:33,387
不安で揺れる心を上手くチューニングして
Successfully tuning my heart that wavered with anxiety

1078
01:16:33,387 --> 01:16:39,087
ほんの小さな勇気を 握りしめていたよ
I was clutching onto a tiny bit of courage

1079
01:16:39,587 --> 01:16:45,087
諦めの文字 手放して進む
Letting go of the word "surrender" and moving forward

1080
01:16:45,087 --> 01:16:52,687
苦しい時も もう私は一人じゃないから
Because even in painful times, I'm not alone anymore

1081
01:16:52,687 --> 01:16:59,087
だからこそ夢追いかけたい ワクワク止まらない
That's why I want to chase my dreams, the excitement won't stop

1082
01:16:59,087 --> 01:17:05,387
想像を超えてく 世界見せてあげる
I'll show you a world that exceeds your imagination

1083
01:17:05,387 --> 01:17:10,787
アクセスしてみてみたい 後悔なんてそうさせない
I want to try accessing it, I won't let you have any regrets

1084
01:17:10,787 --> 01:17:18,187
それぞれ違った 心で走れよ
Run forward with our individual hearts!

1085
01:17:22,687 --> 01:17:28,087
夜空に輝く眩しい思いは
The dazzling feelings shining in the night sky

1086
01:17:28,087 --> 01:17:33,387
見たこともない光を リアルに届けるよ
Will deliver a light you've never seen before to reality

1087
01:17:33,887 --> 01:17:39,387
いつも聞こえるエールをここにキャプチャーして
Capturing the cheers I always hear right here

1088
01:17:39,387 --> 01:17:45,087
また新しい光を 探したくなるよ
It makes me want to look for a new light again

1089
01:17:45,387 --> 01:17:50,887
君の笑顔は 誇らしく進む
Your smile moves forward proudly

1090
01:17:50,887 --> 01:17:58,587
悲しい時に 見返すよ力湧くから
When I'm sad, I'll look back at it, because it gives me strength

1091
01:17:58,587 --> 01:18:05,087
胸を張って夢追いかけたい 奇跡のストーリー
I want to puff out my chest and chase my dreams, a miraculous story

1092
01:18:05,087 --> 01:18:11,387
一緒に作ろう 終わらない夢を
Let's create an endless dream together

1093
01:18:11,387 --> 01:18:16,887
誰一人欠かせない 相まったこの世界
In this world where everyone is indispensable and intertwined

1094
01:18:16,887 --> 01:18:24,587
それぞれ違った 心で彩れ
Color it with our individual hearts!

1095
01:18:33,587 --> 01:18:36,587
悲しい時も
Even when it's sad

1096
01:18:36,587 --> 01:18:39,587
寂しい時も
Even when it's lonely

1097
01:18:39,587 --> 01:18:44,587
信じ合えるものがある
There's something we can believe in together

1098
01:18:44,587 --> 01:18:50,387
密かにこの鼓動 鳴らし続けたい
Deep down, I want to keep this heartbeat sounding

1099
01:18:50,387 --> 01:18:58,087
モノクロの世界に 溢れ出すよ笑顔たち
Smiles will overflow into this monochrome world

1100
01:18:59,387 --> 01:19:04,887
憧れの舞台立ちたい まぶしく輝きたい
I want to stand on the stage I've longed for, I want to shine dazzlingly

1101
01:19:04,887 --> 01:19:10,687
時になみだして また笑い合いたい
Sometimes we'll cry, but I want us to laugh together again

1102
01:19:10,687 --> 01:19:16,387
同じ未来を見ていたい あの夢手にしたい
I want to see the same future, I want to grasp that dream

1103
01:19:16,387 --> 01:19:23,087
踏み出そう 奇跡の一歩を
Let's take a step, a miraculous step

1104
01:19:23,387 --> 01:19:29,687
息切らして夢追いかけたい ワクワク止まらない
Running out of breath, I want to chase my dreams, the excitement won't stop

1105
01:19:29,687 --> 01:19:35,987
想像を超えてく 世界見せてあげる
I'll show you a world that exceeds your imagination

1106
01:19:35,987 --> 01:19:41,387
アクセスしてみてみない？ 後悔なんてここにはない
Won't you try accessing it? There are no regrets here

1107
01:19:41,387 --> 01:19:48,587
それぞれ違った 心で作るよ
We'll create it with our individual hearts!

1108
01:20:12,875 --> 01:20:14,575
みんな、コークは持ったかな？
Everyone, got your Cokes?

1109
01:20:14,575 --> 01:20:15,575
持ちましたー！
Got them!

1110
01:20:15,575 --> 01:20:16,775
乾杯するー！
Let's toast!

1111
01:20:16,775 --> 01:20:18,675
こら、こら、早いよ、ラプちゃん。
Hey, hey, too early, Lapu-chan.

1112
01:20:18,675 --> 01:20:19,875
避けるな、当たる！
Don't dodge, it'll hit!

1113
01:20:19,875 --> 01:20:22,475
年越しのタイミングでみんなで
「乾杯」ってするんだよ。
We're all going to say "Cheers"
at the turn of the year.

1114
01:20:22,475 --> 01:20:24,875
やだやだ、もう喉カラカラ。
No, no, my throat is already parched.

1115
01:20:24,875 --> 01:20:26,875
楽しみだね。
I'm so excited.

1116
01:20:26,875 --> 01:20:28,075
ね、みこさん？
Right, Miko-san?

1117
01:20:28,075 --> 01:20:29,075
みこさん？
Miko-san?

1118
01:20:29,475 --> 01:20:31,775
いやー、いいライブだったね。
Wow, that was a great live.

1119
01:20:31,775 --> 01:20:33,475
お疲れ。
Good job.

1120
