滲む空ピンクはバラ色
The blurry pink sky is rose-colored

1412
01:37:58,692 --> 01:38:02,292
どれだけうまく見せようとしても
No matter how well you try to show it

1413
01:38:02,292 --> 01:38:04,892
君がいなければ　何の味もない
Without you, it has no flavor

1414
01:38:04,892 --> 01:38:08,592
かすり傷すらつかない幻想
An illusion that doesn't even leave a scratch

1415
01:38:08,592 --> 01:38:12,292
針の落ちないレコードさ
Like a record with no needle dropping

1416
01:38:12,292 --> 01:38:15,992
高い熱度で色づいて
Colored by intense heat

1417
01:38:15,992 --> 01:38:17,592
風を背にして
With the wind at my back

1418
01:38:17,592 --> 01:38:19,092
Come let's run

1419
01:38:19,092 --> 01:38:22,192
外へと吹き荒れる
Blowing wildly outward

1420
01:38:22,192 --> 01:38:24,292
向かい風にも心
Even in the headwind, my heart

1421
01:38:24,292 --> 01:38:25,892
靡かせて
Letting it flutter

1422
01:38:25,892 --> 01:38:29,192
飛び出せ to the future
Leap out to the future

1423
01:38:29,192 --> 01:38:32,592
ライン際だって　荒らしにしか見えない
Even on the edge, it only looks like a storm

1424
01:38:32,592 --> 01:38:35,892
ときめいてしまえば
If you feel the excitement

1425
01:38:35,892 --> 01:38:39,692
瞬く間に広がる開放
Release spreading in the blink of an eye

1426
01:38:39,692 --> 01:38:43,492
一つ一つ全てがドラマ
Each and every thing is a drama

1427
01:38:43,492 --> 01:38:47,192
街は見た DEV_IS The Light
The city saw DEV_IS The Light

1428
01:38:47,192 --> 01:38:49,992
変わる変わる色づくパノラマ
The changing, changing colored panorama

1429
01:38:49,992 --> 01:38:53,892
満ち溢れる フィーリンググラデーション
Overflowing Feeling Gradation

1430
01:38:53,892 --> 01:38:57,392
飛び出せ you make me high
Leap out, you make me high

1431
01:38:57,392 --> 01:39:00,592
恐れるものはない The Light
There is nothing to fear, The Light

1432
01:39:00,592 --> 01:39:04,492
綺麗ださ夜明けが
The dawn is beautiful

1433
01:39:04,492 --> 01:39:08,492
どんな明日も照らすよ
It will illuminate any tomorrow

1434
01:39:14,892 --> 01:39:18,892
Ah...

1435
01:39:19,892 --> 01:39:22,392
Mr. The Light, Hey!

1436
01:39:24,292 --> 01:39:26,692
ありがとうございました！
Thank you very much!

1437
01:39:26,892 --> 01:39:28,892
最後の曲は...
The last song is...

1438
01:39:28,892 --> 01:39:31,392
Our Bright Parade!

1439
01:39:31,392 --> 01:39:33,892
イエーイ！
Yay!

1440
01:39:51,692 --> 01:39:55,092
パレード、パレード、パレード
Parade, parade, parade

1441
01:39:55,092 --> 01:39:58,192
輝くんだよ
I'm going to shine

1442
01:39:58,192 --> 01:40:01,392
呼び合う声を合図に
With calling voices as the signal

1443
01:40:06,007 --> 01:40:08,807
パレパレパレ
Parade, parade, parade

1444
01:40:08,807 --> 01:40:11,407
探しに行く
We go to find it

1445
01:40:11,807 --> 01:40:17,007
スカートはラウンドだって
Our skirts go round and round

1446
01:40:38,407 --> 01:40:42,807
まだ 独り言 続いた
My monologue still continued

1447
01:40:43,307 --> 01:40:47,607
ただ 始めたくて 走った
I ran, just wanting to start

1448
01:40:48,107 --> 01:40:52,607
遠く 暗がりに 灯った
A light in the distant darkness

1449
01:40:53,007 --> 01:40:57,407
それは 眩しすぎた 名前
It was a name far too bright

1450
01:40:58,307 --> 01:41:02,807
それは 優しすぎる 思い出
They are memories far too kind

1451
01:41:03,107 --> 01:41:05,807
もっと 近づけと 手を伸ばした
I reached out to get closer

1452
01:41:06,707 --> 01:41:09,007
思いがけず 結び合った
We unexpectedly joined hands

1453
01:41:09,207 --> 01:41:13,407
ほら 今 迷い子は 僕らになった
Look, now the lost children have become us

1454
01:41:14,507 --> 01:41:18,807
パレパレパレ 輝くんだよ
Parade, parade, parade, let's shine

1455
01:41:19,307 --> 01:41:23,807
悔しさも 愛しさも 全て おいで
Regrets and affection, bring them all along

1456
01:41:24,507 --> 01:41:28,807
風 夢 羽 飛び立てるさ
With wind, dreams, and wings, we can take flight

1457
01:41:29,207 --> 01:41:32,507
ささやかな 祝いの光
A small light of celebration

1458
01:41:33,007 --> 01:41:35,007
終わりなき 日差し
Endless sunlight

1459
01:41:35,407 --> 01:41:39,707
君を見つけたこと 胸を張れるよ
Finding you is something I can be proud of

1460
01:41:40,207 --> 01:41:44,807
ここから これから Our Bright Parade
From here, from now on, Our Bright Parade

1461
01:41:55,407 --> 01:41:59,807
まだ 頼りない 横顔
Still an uncertain profile

1462
01:42:00,207 --> 01:42:04,507
歌を 恥ずかしくって 泣いた
I cried because I was embarrassed to sing

1463
01:42:05,007 --> 01:42:09,807
誰も 解けない 暇に
In a time that no one can unravel

1464
01:42:10,107 --> 01:42:14,607
いつか また 会える おまじない
A lucky charm to meet again someday

1465
01:42:15,107 --> 01:42:20,407
あの日 手のひらに 始まった ストーリー
A story that began in our palms that day

1466
01:42:20,907 --> 01:42:23,407
数えきれない 言の葉
Countless words

1467
01:42:23,607 --> 01:42:25,807
数えるような 思いじゃないさ
They aren't feelings you can just count

1468
01:42:26,107 --> 01:42:30,407
ほら 今 僕らを ひとつと 呼ぼう
Look, now let's call us one

1469
01:42:31,507 --> 01:42:35,807
パレパレパレ 美しいんだよ
Parade, parade, parade, it's beautiful

1470
01:42:36,407 --> 01:42:41,007
許し合える 切ない夜は 煌めく
Painful nights when we forgive each other sparkle

1471
01:42:41,507 --> 01:42:46,007
雨 晴れ カレ 待ってた空
Rain, sun, the sky we were waiting for

1472
01:42:46,307 --> 01:42:48,807
相応しい 旅路とは
What makes a worthy journey

1473
01:42:49,007 --> 01:42:53,307
君と歩くことさ
Is walking with you

1474
01:42:54,007 --> 01:42:58,407
君と歩くことなんだ
Is walking with you

1475
01:42:59,007 --> 01:43:02,807
「ただいま」を聞けば
If I hear "I'm home"

1476
01:43:02,807 --> 01:43:06,607
「おかえり」って 叫ぶよ
I'll shout "Welcome back!"

1477
01:43:07,307 --> 01:43:11,407
当たり前じゃないか
Isn't that obvious?

1478
01:43:13,507 --> 01:43:17,807
パレパレパレ 輝くんだよ
Parade, parade, parade, let's shine

1479
01:43:18,307 --> 01:43:23,607
暗がりを 満たすのは 君だ 僕だ
The ones filling the darkness are you and me

1480
01:43:24,507 --> 01:43:28,807
パレパレパレ 輝くんだよ
Parade, parade, parade, let's shine

1481
01:43:29,207 --> 01:43:33,807
悔しさも 愛しさも 全て おいで
Regrets and affection, bring them all along

1482
01:43:35,007 --> 01:43:39,207
風 夢 羽 飛び立てるさ
With wind, dreams, and wings, we can take flight

1483
01:43:40,007 --> 01:43:42,207
ささやかな 祝いの光
A small light of celebration

1484
01:43:42,507 --> 01:43:44,807
終わりなき 日差し
Endless sunlight

1485
01:43:45,107 --> 01:43:47,807
君と飛び込んだよ
I jumped in with you

1486
01:43:47,807 --> 01:43:49,807
素敵な スタートさ
It's a wonderful start

1487
01:43:50,207 --> 01:43:54,807
ここから これから Our Bright Parade
From here, from now on, Our Bright Parade

